ygData.subject: A good place
ygData.msgSnippet: Where is a good place for a Lvl 18 Cleric and a Lvl 18 Monk to go get good exp and good loot?  As of now we re in Lake Rathe but haven t gotten to the good
ygData.messageBody:
Where is a good place for a Lvl 18 Cleric and a Lvl 18 Monk to go get good
exp and good loot? As of now we're in Lake Rathe but haven't gotten to the
good stuff yet cause it was daytime. But I'm not to sure we want to take
the trip back over just to go to Unrest right now, maybe in a few days but I
think we kinda wanna stay on the side we're on till maybe Lvl 19 or 20.
We're wanting a place to get Lvls kinda fast at least till 20 but it doesn't
matter to me how fast we move up in lvls right now just want a place we can
get exp.

**************************
Azor
Lvl 18 Human Cleric of the Rathe
**************************
